<i> Just one problem,</i>
<i> tapes cost a fortune,</i>

00:08.342 --> 00:09.108
<i> so I only owned two,</i>

00:09.110 --> 00:12.277
<i> both of which were</i>
<i> the</i> Cocktail <i> soundtrack.</i>

