and I love Meadowlark Lemon.

00:47.081 --> 00:49.515
I never thought
the two of them would meet.

00:49.517 --> 00:50.816
(BUZZING)
Damn it!

00:50.818 --> 00:52.251
Can you at least try to--

00:52.253 --> 00:53.385
I hate you and this house.

00:53.387 --> 00:54.420
I didn't even do anything.

00:54.422 --> 00:57.122
