just dented itself.

00:57.124 --> 00:58.057
(BUZZING)
Come on, man!

00:58.059 --> 00:59.525
Like I'm supposed
to believe...
(BUZZING)

00:59.527 --> 01:00.626
BARRY: Why does this
thing keep going off?

01:00.628 --> 01:03.062
