court on the island!

01:03.064 --> 01:04.229
(BARKING)
BEVERLY: My own daughter...

01:04.231 --> 01:05.531
(BUZZING)
BARRY: Damn it!

01:05.533 --> 01:06.899
Damn it! Darn it!

01:06.901 --> 01:07.866
That's obviously stupid.

01:07.868 --> 01:09.168
Apparently...
(BUZZING)

01:09.170 --> 01:12.137
<i> Yep, it seemed I would never</i>
<i> get to enjoy the music I liked</i>

01:12.139 --> 01:16.308
<i> until one company</i>
<i> changed everything.</i>

01:16.310 --> 01:17.042
Columbia house.

01:17.044 --> 01:20.913
My God! How did you
get all those tapes on
a lawn mower's salary?

01:20.915 --> 01:22.714
