01:40.601 --> 01:41.166
Tapes!

01:41.168 --> 01:42.935
ADULT ADAM: <i> It had to be</i>
<i> too good to be true.</i>

01:42.937 --> 01:46.305
<i> So I went to the biggest</i>
<i> con artist in my family,</i>

01:46.307 --> 01:46.905
<i> my big sister.</i>

01:46.907 --> 01:48.841
Sure, you get a bunch
of tapes up front,

01:48.843 --> 01:50.175
but then you enter
into a contract

01:50.177 --> 01:52.111
to order more
for full price.

01:52.113 --> 01:55.514
