too much credit.

02:00.488 --> 02:03.088
Point is, you can't
get something for free.

02:03.090 --> 02:03.989
Sure you can.

02:03.991 --> 02:04.823
What you do is
go into a store,

02:04.825 --> 02:06.692
take a bunch of stuff,
and then just walk out.

02:06.694 --> 02:07.726
Yeah,
that's called stealing.

02:07.728 --> 02:09.128
(MOCKING)
That's called stealing.

02:09.130 --> 02:10.829
That's what
you sound like.

02:10.831 --> 02:11.296
Wait, wait.

02:11.298 --> 02:14.366
What if I give Columbia House
a fake name

02:14.368 --> 02:15.467
and take the 12 tapes?

02:15.469 --> 02:17.970
Well, it's illegal,
but very clever.

02:17.972 --> 02:18.804
