02:25.613 --> 02:27.412
It'll be a good
bonding experience,

02:27.414 --> 02:29.248
or at the very least
a cautionary tale.

02:29.250 --> 02:32.184
Whoa. Your little
brother's hardcore.

02:32.186 --> 02:33.452
Yeah, a hardcore nerd.

02:33.454 --> 02:34.419
