<i> I feel the need to say</i>

02:50.070 --> 02:50.802
<i> ¶ I don't know the future</i>

02:50.804 --> 02:55.574
<i> ¶ But the past keeps getting</i>
<i> clearer every day ¶</i>

02:55.843 --> 02:58.277
<i> It was March 16,</i>
<i> 1980-something,</i>

02:58.279 --> 03:01.013
<i> and my brother went to pick up</i>
<i> his girlfriend, Lainey.</i>

03:01.015 --> 03:04.983
<i> One problem, he had to</i>
<i> get by her dad first.</i>

03:05.052 --> 03:05.517
Lainey!

03:05.519 --> 03:08.187
The screamy kid with
the crazy eyebrows is here.

03:08.189 --> 03:10.889
Special night.
It's our 10-month anniversary.

03:10.891 --> 03:13.025
Anniversaries are for years,
not months,

03:13.027 --> 03:15.060
so you're celebrating
nothing.

03:15.062 --> 03:16.528
