(CLEARS THROAT)

03:36.684 --> 03:37.182
(CHUCKLES)

03:37.184 --> 03:39.117
If that jacket hits the floor
tonight, so do you.

03:39.119 --> 03:40.586
Okay, kids,
have a great time.

03:40.588 --> 03:42.788
<i> Even though Barry had won</i>
<i> the love of his life,</i>

03:42.790 --> 03:46.291
