03:47.161 --> 03:49.761
Nothing like a cold one
after work, am I right?

03:49.763 --> 03:50.462
Amen to that, brother!

03:50.464 --> 03:53.565
Love me the old brew ha-ha,
nectar of the gods,

03:53.567 --> 03:56.568
foam hammer, wheat and greet,
little truth water,

03:56.570 --> 03:59.271
