beer.

03:59.273 --> 04:01.139
Move over, rover.

04:01.141 --> 04:02.975
Are you telling me you drink?
No!

04:02.977 --> 04:05.077
You just said
you love cold suds.

04:05.079 --> 04:07.846
So which is it?
Are you a lush or a liar?

04:07.848 --> 04:10.482
He's a moron.
I'm gonna grab us
a refill, Mur.

04:10.484 --> 04:12.918
You want a six pack,
Mickey Mantle?

04:12.920 --> 04:14.019
Mmm-mmm.

