04:34.508 --> 04:36.074
So it's not personal.

04:36.076 --> 04:37.175
Yes!

04:37.177 --> 04:38.010
Top shelf.

04:38.012 --> 04:39.444
Yeah, throw this away.
No.

04:39.446 --> 04:41.079
