infinite fake names

04:53.961 --> 04:54.993
and get all the tapes?

04:54.995 --> 04:57.195
Are you sure
this is a good idea?

04:57.197 --> 04:58.897
I've thought of everything,
Erica.

04:58.899 --> 05:01.800
See, Columbia House
has agents everywhere

05:01.802 --> 05:03.001
looking to collect
their money.

05:03.003 --> 05:05.971
