05:56.657 --> 05:59.091
How did you get the money
for all that?

05:59.093 --> 06:00.292
Do you want to
ask questions?

06:00.294 --> 06:02.928
Or do you want a little
Neil Diamond?

06:03.464 --> 06:04.229
I saw nothing.

06:04.231 --> 06:06.998
