while you two were dating?

06:43.771 --> 06:45.337
I thought he hated me
'cause I'm your boyfriend.

06:45.339 --> 06:48.607
Oh, sweetie, no.
My dad hates you as,
like, a person.

06:48.609 --> 06:51.209
You being my boyfriend
is just a happy coincidence.

06:51.211 --> 06:51.843
Well, don't worry.

06:51.845 --> 06:55.046
I know a man who's got
the inside track on your dad,

06:55.048 --> 06:58.617
and he'll be more than
happy to help me.

06:58.619 --> 07:01.453
Mmm, yeah, uh...

07:01.455 --> 07:04.322
What is that?
Is that a yes or a no?

07:04.324 --> 07:05.991
