07:52.272 --> 07:54.639
<i> And so my brother was</i>
<i> scheming to win over Bill.</i>

07:54.641 --> 07:58.243
<i> Meanwhile, my mom was</i>
<i> about to get wise</i>
<i> to my scheme.</i>

07:58.245 --> 08:00.278
Got a package
for Papa Smurfenstein.

08:00.280 --> 08:02.047
