to get free tapes.

08:22.603 --> 08:26.438
Well, I think it's obvious
who's responsible.

08:26.640 --> 08:27.839
Me?
Yes, you.

08:27.841 --> 08:29.040
Who else would it be?

08:29.042 --> 08:30.008
ERICA: Kermit D. Fonz?

08:30.010 --> 08:31.510
That's got Adam
written all over it.

08:31.512 --> 08:35.013
