that Adam did this?
Yes.

08:35.015 --> 08:36.214
Adam?
Adam.

08:36.216 --> 08:37.716
My delicious little
snuggle monster?

08:37.718 --> 08:39.217
Yes, Adam.
Adam?

08:39.219 --> 08:41.253
He's guilty.
Tell her you're guilty.

08:41.255 --> 08:43.722
Why does she say
these things, Mama?

08:43.724 --> 08:44.956
I'm just a little boy.

08:44.958 --> 08:47.659
See? He has an alibi.
He's a little boy.

08:47.661 --> 08:49.561
Why do you always blame me
for everything?

08:49.563 --> 08:51.496
Just open the box
and look at the tapes,

08:51.498 --> 08:53.465
