It was such a good deal.

09:18.725 --> 09:20.492
I got caught
in the heat of the moment.

09:20.494 --> 09:23.194
Which is also a song I got
for a fraction of a penny.

09:23.196 --> 09:25.964
Shh, you don't have to
lie for her anymore.

09:25.966 --> 09:27.165
Seriously?
What?

09:27.167 --> 09:29.167
Let mama make you
a banana split.

09:29.169 --> 09:31.836
(CHUCKLES) Okay?
You get nothing.

09:31.972 --> 09:34.072
Oof, tough break.

09:34.374 --> 09:36.474
